'''皮耶·尼內'''（{{lang-fr|{{lang-fr|Pierre Niney}}}}；{{bd|1989年|3月13日}}），是一名法國男演員，他以2014年的傳記電影《[[時尚大師聖羅蘭|時尚大師聖羅蘭]]》中飾演設計師[[伊夫·圣洛朗|伊夫·圣洛朗]]而獲得[[凱薩獎最佳男主角獎|凱薩獎最佳男主角獎]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Sowray |first=Bibby |url=http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/columns/bibby-sowray/TMG10558923/Pierre-Berges-praise-for-YSL-biopic.html |title=Pierre Berge's praise for YSL biopic |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=8 January 2014 |accessdate=9 February 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221205918/http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/columns/bibby-sowray/TMG10558923/Pierre-Berges-praise-for-YSL-biopic.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/frances-cesar-awards-nominations-announced-767682|title=Juliette Binoche, Marion Cotillard, Kristen Stewart Among France's Cesar Awards Nominees|accessdate=29 January 2015|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707034409/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/frances-cesar-awards-nominations-announced-767682|dead-url=no}}</ref>

